              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/23028649/" class="">日軍射擊訓練</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/maynepaddy/" class=" " title="Mayne Katze">Mayne Katze</a>
                (無產階級餵貓騎士)
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
